    "task_id": "202605100837-PGH61Q",
    "title": "Pre-v0.5: split hook capabilities and declare write intent",
    "intent": "Classify hooks into read-only checks and write-capable enforcement. Read-only hooks should avoid index writes; write-capable hooks must take the worktree mutex or write outside the Git index. Push hooks must not create lifecycle/status commits implicitly.",
